Package au.gov.sbr.core.requester.exceptions

Class Summary
 

Exception Summary
SBRCommunicationException SBR Communication Exception is used for all communication errors between web service and client except Timeout.
SBRCoreException SBR Core Exception class.
SBRException SBR Exception is the parent class of all related SBR Core Service Requester component exceptions.
SBRReceiverException SBR Receiver Exception is used for all related SOAP Fault exceptions that originate from the receiver.
SBRSenderException SBR Sender Exception is used for all related SOAP Fault exceptions that originate from the sender.
SBRTimeoutException SBR Timeout Exception is used for all Timeout errors between web service and client.
SBRUnavailableException SBR Communication Exception is used for all service unavailable errors between web service and client.
